# Notifications

**Figma:** [Notifications](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10527&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, variants, semantic types, and token mappings below are derived from Figma node 128:10527.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Message container | `--bg-base-default` |
| Message icon/title | `--text-base-default` |
| Message body | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Message close | `--text-brand-default` |
| Message button | `--bg-brand-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Alert container | `--bg-danger-tertiary` |
| Alert icon/close | `--text-danger-default` |
| Alert button | `--bg-danger-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Success | `--bg-success-tertiary`, `--text-success-default`, `--bg-success-default` |
| Warning | `--bg-warning-tertiary`, `--text-warning-default`, `--bg-warning-default` |
| Info | `--bg-brand-tertiary`, `--text-brand-default`, `--bg-brand-default` |

