## Structure (shared)

| Element | Position | Token |
|---------|----------|-------|
| Icon | Left of title | Info (ⓘ) or semantic |
| Title | Bold | `--text-base-default` |
| Body text | Below title | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Close button | Top-right | "X" icon |
| CTA button | Below body | Primary style |

---

## Variants

### Message (informational)
- **Container:** `--bg-base-default`; rounded corners.
- **Icon:** `--text-base-default`.
- **Title/body:** `--text-base-default`, `--text-base-secondary`.
- **Close:** `--text-brand-default`.
- **Button:** `--bg-brand-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text.
- **Use:** General information, success.

### Alert (warning/error)
- **Container:** `--bg-danger-tertiary`.
- **Icon:** `--text-danger-default`.
- **Title/body:** `--text-base-default`, `--text-base-secondary`.
- **Close:** `--text-danger-default`.
- **Button:** `--bg-danger-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text.
- **Use:** Warnings, errors, critical information.

### Semantic variants
| Type | Container | Icon | Button |
|------|-----------|------|--------|
| Success | `--bg-success-tertiary` | `--text-success-default` | `--bg-success-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Warning | `--bg-warning-tertiary` | `--text-warning-default` | `--bg-warning-default` |
| Info | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | `--text-brand-default` | `--bg-brand-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |

---

## Spacing

- Space/200–300 between icon and title.
- Space/400 between sections.
- Padding: Space/200–400.

---

## Toast (temporary)

- Position: fixed top-4 right-4; z-50.
- Auto-dismiss: 3–5 seconds.
- Stack vertically with 8px gap.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10527.
